&lt;p&gt;This is a highly autonomous role with meaningful ownership over customer outcomes and commercial results. You’ll collaborate closely with Sales, Implementation, Support, and Product, while also shaping how BrightHire serves its Mid-Market customers through feedback, iteration, and continuous improvement. It’s an opportunity to have real influence — on your customers’ hiring outcomes and on the evolution of BrightHire’s customer success motion.&lt;/p&gt;
