&lt;p&gt;This is a role for an engineer with strong product taste, customer empathy, and the ability to make LLMs useful in real workflows. You care deeply about output quality, speed, accuracy, safety, and tone and you know how to iterate until the experience feels genuinely valuable to end users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
