&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Voice AI interviewers&lt;/span&gt; that create structured, high-quality candidate conversations and assessments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Automatic interview coaching&lt;/span&gt; that provides tailored feedback and guidance based on an interviewer’s recent interviews, with customizable content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;AI candidate skills matrices&lt;/span&gt; that summarize evidence from interviews and map it to key skills aligned with the job description.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;AI assistants&lt;/span&gt; that let users instantly query any detail about a candidate, interview, or hiring process using natural language.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Customizable interview summaries&lt;/span&gt; that enable customers to generate personalized summaries using their own structure, criteria, and tone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And many more AI-native workflows that help hiring teams make better decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
